data.meta_description: Albania, officially The Republic of Albania, is a country in Europe, with an area of 28,748 square kilometers and a population of around 2,845,955. Its gdp is $15,278.08 Millions(2019). The capital of Albania Tirana, and the official currency is Albanian Lek(ALL).
data.text:
Albania, officially The Republic of Albania, is a country in Europe, with an area of 28,748 square kilometers and a population of around 2,845,955. Its gdp is $15,278.08 Millions(2019). The capital of Albania Tirana, and the official currency is Albanian Lek(ALL).
